
Overview of noun adjustment

The noun adjustment has 5 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (5) adjustment, accommodation, fitting -- (making or becoming suitable; adjusting to circumstances)
2. (3) alteration, modification, adjustment -- (the act of making something different (as e.g. the size of a garment))
3. (1) adjustment, registration, readjustment -- (the act of adjusting something to match a standard)
4. adaptation, adaption, adjustment -- (the process of adapting to something (such as environmental conditions))
5. allowance, adjustment -- (an amount added or deducted on the basis of qualifying circumstances; "an allowance for profit")
